metadata.name: Bitcoin Old Coins #01
metadata.description:
Once upon a time, there was a cryptocurrency enthusiast, an old man who had hid a chest full of bitcoins at the bottom of a river. One day, during a drought, a team of treasure hunters found the ancient chest. They were surprised to find the chest full of valuable bitcoins! And just like that, they became millionaires overnight.

The story has become legendary and is remembered as an example of how incredible the cryptocurrency appreciation can be, even when long forgotten.
